    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "m0QcAE3J+iZV4kJHdUlgPCLMoR1y3kRhWGgxHkrRxqE=",
    "originContent": "## About",
    "translatedContent": "## 关于"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "GYoVnuiOVf+SYSJ7WAxxw1SLF1ZekkYlixtJh//BKTE=",
    "originContent": "Altbot is an open-source accessibility bot designed to enhance the Fediverse by generating alt-text descriptions for images, video, and audio. This helps make content more accessible to users with visual impairments.",
    "translatedContent": "Altbot 是一个开源无障碍机器人，旨在通过为图片、视频和音频生成替代文本描述来增强联邦宇宙的可访问性。这样有助于视觉障碍用户更容易访问内容。"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "F3w6vVN5ebgz/LpBcIIan/bO73ASB3VUVKyeknwUwpQ=",
    "originContent": "## Privacy & GDPR Compliance",
    "translatedContent": "## 隐私与 GDPR 合规"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "LiXxjjYXqkMFlYyPYVMR1bpaDT4tvJglrNuB58hQotQ=",
    "originContent": "**Altbot 2.0 now processes everything 100% locally with zero data retention!** [![Mastodon Follow](https://img.shields.io/mastodon/follow/113183205946060973?domain=fuzzies.wtf&style=social)](https://fuzzies.wtf/@altbot)",
    "translatedContent": "**Altbot 2.0 现已实现所有处理100%本地完成，零数据保留！** [![Mastodon 关注](https://img.shields.io/mastodon/follow/113183205946060973?domain=fuzzies.wtf&style=social)](https://fuzzies.wtf/@altbot)"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "UpMcNp1DoB2ndtR94nE6deSzHqCEekoFqlBglz5W8qI=",
    "originContent": "In compliance with GDPR, Altbot requires explicit informed consent before processing any user requests. When you interact with Altbot for the first time, you'll receive a consent request with information about data collection practices and a link to our [Privacy Policy](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/micr0-dev/Altbot/main/PRIVACY.md).",
    "translatedContent": "为符合 GDPR，Altbot 在处理任何用户请求前需要明确的知情同意。首次与 Altbot 互动时，您将收到同意请求，包含数据收集实践的信息及我们的[隐私政策](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/micr0-dev/Altbot/main/PRIVACY.md)链接。"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "/mP50c7cMr+Pf88OvIJTQCviMjQkbImRbC1EZ2Sy7H8=",
    "originContent": "- **What we collect:** Request timestamps, processing times, language preferences, media type",
    "translatedContent": "- **我们收集的信息：** 请求时间戳、处理时间、语言偏好、媒体类型"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "O1gokAxBTRwcx4V/cZ2YihDX7BHdTefM/Y2kgfu6I50=",
    "originContent": "- **What we don't collect:** Images, personal information, content of your posts",
    "translatedContent": "- **我们不收集的信息：** 图片、个人信息、帖子内容"
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "z0jjxdDT83DEOXsVoyuDaRVxvPFQrn/HdBBLXbzpBD4=",
    "originContent": "- **How to revoke consent:** Simply block the bot account",
    "translatedContent": "- **如何撤回同意：** 只需屏蔽该机器人账号"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "MwlFKoUHUMThc4XeoSd1gAI2y/THKVClB0AqPb2spgY=",
    "originContent": "Your post content is never saved or shared. Only images without existing alt-text will be processed, and all processing happens privately on our local server.",
    "translatedContent": "您的帖子内容绝不会被保存或分享。只有没有现有替代文本的图片会被处理，且所有处理均在我们的本地服务器私密完成。"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "aU2AoMUV45em9//+jYmdfv83JGc0QNF5oAwpldQ5sVo=",
    "originContent": "## Disclaimer",
    "translatedContent": "## 免责声明"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "6JHWzgUVC/bqxJu7SFjVzuie238fMHr6gmQU2okDtdA=",
    "originContent": "Alt-texts are generated using a Large Language Model (LLM). While we strive for accuracy, results may sometimes be factually incorrect. Always double-check the alt-text before using it.",
    "translatedContent": "替代文本由大型语言模型（LLM）生成。虽然我们力求准确，但结果有时可能存在事实错误。请务必在使用前仔细核对替代文本。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "8Cn7DTPwgC5TRYcpx6IHELZx2Ghn/Zy5V2CaSviu4ik=",
    "originContent": "## How It Works",
    "translatedContent": "## 工作原理"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "f0QoZc129E/Y9XiakhKWxzg4uEBrcYfXiSF4CRR5CoQ=",
    "originContent": "Altbot listens for mentions and follows on Mastodon. When it detects a mention or a new post from a followed user, it checks for images without alt-text. If it finds any, it uses a Large Language Model (LLM) to generate descriptive alt-text and replies with the generated text.",
    "translatedContent": "Altbot 监听 Mastodon 上的提及和关注。当检测到提及或关注用户的新帖子时，会检查是否有无替代文本的图片。如果发现，会使用大型语言模型（LLM）生成描述性的替代文本并回复生成的文本。"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "Va7ER4dHPfmt1CvLSeep2AEpy33nUzxb+6qMZz++7BQ=",
    "originContent": "### Features",
    "translatedContent": "### 功能"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "5Y7gqECXECFIlvF49fPvkG6B1m8bskRcYynCr9IPALA=",
    "originContent": "- **Mention-Based Alt-Text Generation:** Mention @Altbot in a reply to any post containing an image, video, or audio, and Altbot will generate an alt-text description for it.",
    "translatedContent": "- **基于提及的替代文本生成：** 在任何包含图片、视频或音频的帖子回复中提及 @Altbot，Altbot 将为其生成替代文本描述。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "ZrYwZdmZlOhhBSbVXs0FrG2PovTnCL0jvt21bxoua3M=",
    "originContent": "- **Automatic Alt-Text for Followers:** Follow @Altbot, and it will monitor your posts. If you post an image, video, or audio without alt-text, Altbot will automatically generate one for you.",
    "translatedContent": "- **为关注者自动生成替代文本：** 关注 @Altbot，它会监控你的帖子。如果你发布了没有替代文本的图片、视频或音频，Altbot 会自动为你生成替代文本。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "fcPS4M7F7Dl3Ig2cRCgjAM2816AZT6jtSpAvO4WCSUA=",
    "originContent": "- **Local LLM Support:** Use local LLMs via Ollama for generating alt-text descriptions.",
    "translatedContent": "- **本地大语言模型支持：** 通过 Ollama 使用本地大语言模型生成替代文本描述。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "2iPXaNlvGaTXKpt1rWZ0QDXP8n366YcSaWIyUAEfU/o=",
    "originContent": "- **GDPR Compliance:** Explicit informed consent system that requires users to provide consent before processing their requests, with clear information about data usage.",
    "translatedContent": "- **符合 GDPR 规定：** 明确的知情同意系统，要求用户在处理请求前提供同意，并清晰告知数据使用情况。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "69JxK7haXBDrhUUlJqxsKPCeHmUbG5OdIN+9AMz4iag=",
    "originContent": "- **Consent Requests:** Ask for consent from the original poster before generating alt-text when mentioned by non-OP users.",
    "translatedContent": "- **同意请求：** 当非原帖用户提及时，生成替代文本前会向原帖发布者请求同意。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "+XeSbwMSrKEPzQ4fQRFXo1cjDzQ+xibCrts45GgjVks=",
    "originContent": "- **Configurable Settings:** Easily configure the bot using a TOML file.",
    "translatedContent": "- **可配置设置：** 通过 TOML 文件轻松配置机器人。  "
  },
  {
